        {
            "title": "歐霸｜曼聯般奴成沙特球隊獵物 魯賓艾摩廉：全力留住他",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"曼聯隊長般奴費南迪斯成希拉爾的獵物。Reuters\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/db6195dbe12abee6e62c3c6a95a9a45b/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250508/_2025050812085784159.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">曼聯隊長般奴費南迪斯成希拉爾的獵物。Reuters</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>近日盛傳曼聯隊長般奴費南迪斯成為沙特球隊希拉爾的獵物，並不惜支付天價轉會費。曼聯領隊魯賓艾摩廉於周三出席歐霸4強次回合對畢爾包的賽前記者會被問到相關傳聞時，明言希望全力留人。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"曼聯隊長般奴費南迪斯成希拉爾的獵物。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a873c4bb89922efb6a286ed64ac39dbd/2025-05/2025-05-01T195356Z_399737212_UP1EL511J9UKO_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-EUROPA-ATH-MUN-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        曼聯隊長般奴費南迪斯成希拉爾的獵物。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"曼聯隊長般奴費南迪斯成希拉爾的獵物。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/fd25144b4fa6bd3784a5f79ff5f28cd5/2025-05/2025-05-01T195029Z_1604425339_UP1EL511J43KI_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-EUROPA-ATH-MUN-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        曼聯隊長般奴費南迪斯成希拉爾的獵物。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"曼聯隊長般奴費南迪斯成希拉爾的獵物。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2d7975f04f62f331c521d8f9b1747492/2025-05/2025-05-01T194952Z_202176898_UP1EL511J33KG_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-EUROPA-ATH-MUN-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        曼聯隊長般奴費南迪斯成希拉爾的獵物。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"曼聯隊長般奴費南迪斯成希拉爾的獵物。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/eb5f16ad15b3bd5b1f907eda7714b663/2025-05/2025-04-17T213350Z_1231530699_UP1EL4H1NWD6Y_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-EUROPA-MUN-OL-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        曼聯隊長般奴費南迪斯成希拉爾的獵物。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"曼聯隊長般奴費南迪斯成希拉爾的獵物。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c15d2725c0d288b3db2d2c61bf435d07/2025-05/2025-04-17T215055Z_462490275_UP1EL4H1OOU7W_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-EUROPA-MUN-OL-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        曼聯隊長般奴費南迪斯成希拉爾的獵物。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"曼聯隊長般奴費南迪斯成希拉爾的獵物。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/50e736baef6a1b7e104eb24ebeea9df5/2025-05/2025-04-17T194035Z_771502849_UP1EL4H1INLZ9_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-EUROPA-MUN-OL-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        曼聯隊長般奴費南迪斯成希拉爾的獵物。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"曼聯隊長般奴費南迪斯成希拉爾的獵物。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e6aa0910fa443f455053ab90ef399f08/2025-05/2025-04-13T165238Z_1585369309_UP1EL4D1AVPA1_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-ENGLAND-NEW-MUN-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        曼聯隊長般奴費南迪斯成希拉爾的獵物。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"魯賓艾摩廉與般奴費南迪斯。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/822b70c0f7f5f2626f8e6b7b7e4367b1/2025-05/2025-04-06T170501Z_1032995577_UP1EL461BGC2Z_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-ENGLAND-MUN-MCI-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        魯賓艾摩廉與般奴費南迪斯。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"魯賓艾摩廉。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/dce74cf232f9ded64be84fb07bd391c2/2025-05/2025-04-06T154615Z_1187882406_UP1EL4617T100_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-ENGLAND-MUN-MCI-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        魯賓艾摩廉。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>傳沙特重金買般奴</h2>\n<p>般奴費南迪斯自加盟曼聯後每季都數據亮麗，今季各賽事亦為曼聯貢獻19個入球和18次助攻。因此，近日傳出此子獲沙特球隊希拉爾相中，準備以超高薪利誘加盟，且願意向曼聯支付天價轉會費。而曼聯正值重建期，需要賣出球員套現組軍，故賣走30歲的般奴絕非不可能。\n\n</p><h2>艾摩廉希望留人</h2>\n<p>不過，主帥艾摩廉就明確表示：「這種轉會傳聞不難理解。般奴會成為轉會市場的熱門話題，不僅是因為他出色的數據，更關鍵是他獨特的比賽風格。他無疑是一名頂級球員，而己隊正需要這樣的頂級球員。他不僅是球隊的核心領袖，更是隊長不二人選。有球隊向般奴招手，這很正常，但我們曼聯希望留住他，畢竟他是當今球壇最強球員之一。」\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
